OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772132672
OL,3,COldest male gorilla in the UK dies
OL,4,Cafter being moved to new home
OL,6,FPictures released by Bristol Zoo
OL,7,FProject after the death of Jock, the
OL,8,Foldest male gorilla in the UK.
OL,10,FThe oldest male gorilla in the UK has
OL,11,Fdied two weeks after being moved to a
OL,12,Fnew habitat at Bristol Zoo Project.
OL,14,FJock, who was 42, had lived at Bristol
OL,15,FZoo for more than 20 years and was the
OL,16,Fzoo's main breeding male.
OL,18,FHe, along with seven other gorillas,
OL,19,Fhad stayed in their existing home
OL,20,Fafter the closure of Bristol Zoo in
OL,21,FSeptember 2022.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
