CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772132672
OL,3,COldest male gorilla in the UK dies
OL,4,Cafter being moved to new home
OL,6,FIn a carefully managed operation they
OL,7,Fwere moved to the zoo's new site in
OL,8,FSouth Gloucestershire several weeks
OL,9,Fago.
OL,11,FSarah Gedman, curator of mammals,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are devastated to share that
OL,13,FJock, our silverback western lowland
OL,14,Fgorilla, has died. Two weeks ago, our
OL,15,Ftroop of eight gorillas were moved
OL,16,Ffrom Bristol Zoo Gardens to their new
OL,17,Fhome at Bristol Zoo Project as part of
OL,18,Fa carefully planned relocation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772132672
OL,3,COldest male gorilla in the UK dies
OL,4,Cafter being moved to new home
OL,6,F"Since the move, our veterinary and
OL,7,Fanimal care teams have continued to
OL,8,Fprovide excellent care and round-the-
OL,9,Fclock monitoring. Jock was the oldest
OL,10,Fmale gorilla in the UK, at 42 years,
OL,11,Fand had a number of pre-existing
OL,12,Fhealth conditions that are common for
OL,13,Fgorillas his age.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772132672
OL,3,COldest male gorilla in the UK dies
OL,4,Cafter being moved to new home
OL,6,F"Jock settled in well to the new
OL,7,Fhabitat, however, 10 days after his
OL,8,Farrival, he experienced a rapid
OL,9,Fdeterioration in health. After a
OL,10,Fdetailed assessment by our veterinary
OL,11,Fand animal care teams, the difficult
OL,12,Fdecision was taken to peacefully
OL,13,Feuthanise Jock, which was the best
OL,14,Foutcome for his welfare.
OL,16,F"We'd like to thank everyone for their
OL,17,Fsympathy as we come to terms with this
OL,18,Fhuge loss and encourage you to share
OL,19,Fyour memories and photos of Jock on
OL,20,Four social media channels. He will be
OL,21,Fso greatly missed by us all."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
