PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772132672
OL,3,COldest male gorilla in the UK dies
OL,4,Cafter being moved to new home
OL,6,FJock, a silverback gorilla, moved to
OL,7,FBristol Zoo in 2003 from London Zoo at
OL,8,Fthe age of 20. As a breeding male he
OL,9,Fhas fathered several baby gorillas.
OL,11,FBristol Zoological Society has cared
OL,12,Ffor gorillas since the 1930s,
OL,13,Fcontributing to the European captive
OL,14,Fbreeding programme.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
